title: Nate And Hayes-Cast: Tommy Lee Jones
description:
Movie Description
A swashbuckling adventure which takes place in the mid-1800&#039;s on the South Pacific islands where bloody raids and battles were once the rule of the day. A notorious buccaneer and a young reverend team up against the villainous ruler of a cutthroat gang.

Credits 
Cast: Tommy Lee Jones 
Director: Ferdinand Fairfax 

Synopsis
Swashbuckling tale of piracy on the high seas when mercenary "good" pirate Captain "Bully" Hayes rescues greenhorn seaman Nathanial and his beautiful bride-to-be Sophie from the clutches of "evil" pirate Ben Pease
